1. *Vojske* su spremne da se bore za našu zemlju. (The armies are ready to fight for our country.)

2. U povijesti su se često vodili ratovi između dvije *vojske*. (In history, wars were often fought between two armies.)

3. *Vojske* su morale biti opremljene da bi bile spremne za rat. (The armies had to be equipped to be ready for war.)

4. Ova dva naroda su imala velike *vojske*. (These two nations had large armies.)

5. U ovoj zemlji je bilo puno *vojski*. (There were many armies in this country.)

6. *Vojske* su se spremale da se bore za slobodu. (The armies were preparing to fight for freedom.)